version_description: bug fixed.
bug fixed.

1. New main menu will appear.
2. 'My info' feature has been added to enable you to check your stats and equipment.
3. A Secret Map opening has been added to the 5-Catch Reward. Secret Map will appear in random when you receive the Catch Reward.
4. You can obtain a treasure of the world in random when you play Secret Map.
5. You can check collected treasure in Treasure. Also, stats will increase when a certain amount is collected.
6. Max Level limited to 70
7. Added new package item
8. Changed Icon
